 a number of\nscenarios including binary supermassive black hole systems, Lense-Thirring\nprecession, and jet precession.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2019 10:37:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 12:30:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
