-instability to the acceleration process\nduring the fast-rise phase of flare-associated PEs in low corona\n($<1.3R_{\\odot}$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2019 15:53:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
